review: Dr Priyanka, a trusted dentist, was recommended to me by a friend. I visited her for a root canal treatment, initially intending to undergo two procedures, but I was a bit nervous. But she was really nice and made me feel comfortable right away. She looked at my teeth carefully and explained everything very clearly. She said we didn't need to do the second root canal, which was a relief. Instead, she filled the tooth, which was a simpler option. She cared about what was best for me, and I'm glad I chose her for my treatment. Her genuine concern for my well-being and her honesty truly impressed me.
reply_text: Thank you for placing your trust in me.Such kind words I am humbled!

review:
I had put off seeing a dentist for a long time due to past experiences at the dentist since childhood. 
Dr. Priyanka came highly recommended by friends and I paid her a visit. Her consultation and treatment fees are very reasonable first and foremost. 
She takes great care in explaining the problem and the route she and her associated colleagues will take to solve the issue. It really puts you at ease. 
Also she puts great emphasis on pain management and to my great surprise, I felt zero pain during and after getting a root canal; a procedure which almost everyone in my life tells me is extremely excruciating. 
If anyone has ever had a fear of the dentist, Dr. Priyanka will change that. I
reply_text: Thank you dear Dr for placing your trust in us. It has been my utmost pleasure in treating and interacting with you!

review:
My experience at Vitalis Dental Care was excellent.
Both Dr. Priyanka & Dr. Karan are efficient, co-operative, polite & friendly when I went to the clinic for extraction of my wisdom tooth. They explained me the things related to tooth extraction & care needed to be taken post extraction in detail. Entire treatment was painless.

The clinic is clean, hygienic & all protocols were followed during the COVID pandemic.
Thanks to the entire team of Vitalis Dental Care.
